---

<html lang="es" class="scroll-smooth">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Portfolio | Carlos Bravo Sánchez</title>
    <style is:global>
        .progress-bar-fill {
            width: 0%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgb(34 197 94);
            transition: width linear;
        }
        .is-animating {
            width: 100% !important;
        }

        /* Lógica visual de la barra lateral contraída (Rail Navigation) */
        #sidebar {
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }
        .sidebar-collapsed {
            width: 5rem !important; /* Estrecha la barra a 80px (w-20) */
        }
        .sidebar-collapsed .sidebar-profile,
        .sidebar-collapsed .sidebar-label,
        .sidebar-collapsed .cv-long {
            display: none;
        }
        .sidebar-collapsed .nav-link {
            justify-content: center;
            padding-left: 0;
            padding-right: 0;
        }
        .sidebar-collapsed .nav-link-icon-wrapper {
            margin-right: 0 !important;
        }
        .sidebar-collapsed .cv-short {
            display: block;
        }
        .cv-short {
            display: none;
        }

        /* ========================================== */
        /* MOTOR DE ESCALADO HÍBRIDO (CSS + JS)       */
        /* ========================================== */
        /* .hero-scaler-container {
            width: 100%;
            overflow: hidden; 
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .hero-scaler {
            width: 100%;
            transform-origin: top center;
        }
        @media (max-width: 1151px) {
            .hero-scaler {
                width: 1152px !important; 
                height: 600px !important; 
                max-width: none !important;
                flex-shrink: 0;
            }
        } */

        /* ========================================== */
        /* ANIMACIÓN CINTA DE HOBBIES (MARQUEE)       */
        /* ========================================== */
        @keyframes scroll-marquee {
            0% { transform: translateX(0); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-50%); } 
        }
        .animate-scroll {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row; /* Fuerza a que todo esté en una sola línea horizontal */
            align-items: flex-start;
            width: max-content; /* Permite que el contenedor crezca más allá de la pantalla */
            animation: scroll-marquee 30s linear infinite;
        }
        .animate-scroll:hover {
            animation-play-state: paused;
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-950 text-gray-200 font-sans selection:bg-green-500 selection:text-black overflow-hidden flex">
    
    <!-- ========================================== -->
    <!-- BARRA LATERAL (SIDEBAR) -->
    <!-- ========================================== -->
    <aside id="sidebar" class="w-64 bg-gray-950 border-r border-gray-800 h-screen flex flex-col justify-between py-6 z-50 flex-shrink-0">
        
        <!-- Botón Hamburguesa -->
        <div class="flex pl-5 mb-4 mt-2">
            <button id="toggle-sidebar" class="p-2 text-gray-500 hover:text-white hover:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path></svg>
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Perfil (Ocultable) -->
        <div class="sidebar-profile flex flex-col items-center px-6 transition-opacity duration-300">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full bg-gray-900 border-2 border-green-500/50 mb-4 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
                <!-- Etiqueta de imagen añadida -->
                <img src="/avatar-sidebar.png" alt="Carlos Bravo" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-white text-center">Carlos Bravo</h1>
            <h2 class="text-sm text-green-500 font-mono mt-1 text-center">Ingeniero Informático</h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Navegación -->
        <nav class="flex flex-col w-full mt-8 px-4 gap-2">
            <a href="#inicio" class="nav-link px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all flex items-center">
                <div class="nav-link-icon-wrapper w-6 flex justify-center mr-3 transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="sidebar-label">Inicio</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#sobre-mi" class="nav-link px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all flex items-center">
                <div class="nav-link-icon-wrapper w-6 flex justify-center mr-3 transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="sidebar-label">Sobre Mí</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#proyectos" class="nav-link px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all flex items-center">
                <div class="nav-link-icon-wrapper w-6 flex justify-center mr-3 transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="sidebar-label">Proyectos</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#en-curso" class="nav-link px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all flex items-center">
                <div class="nav-link-icon-wrapper w-6 flex justify-center mr-3 transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5z"></path><path d="M12 14l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 14l9-5-9-5-9 5 9 5zm0 0l6.16-3.422a12.083 12.083 0 01.665 6.479A11.952 11.952 0 0012 20.055a11.952 11.952 0 00-6.824-2.998 12.078 12.078 0 01.665-6.479L12 14zm-4 6v-7.5l4-2.222"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="sidebar-label">Formación Continua</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#otras-actividades" class="nav-link px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all flex items-center">
                <div class="nav-link-icon-wrapper w-6 flex justify-center mr-3 transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM14 6a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2V6zM4 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2zM14 16a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v2a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="sidebar-label">Otras Actividades</span>
            </a>

            <a href="#contacto" class="nav-link px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-gray-900 transition-all flex items-center">
                <div class="nav-link-icon-wrapper w-6 flex justify-center mr-3 transition-all">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="sidebar-label">Contacto</span>
            </a>
        </nav>

        <!-- Botón CV Dinámico -->
        <div class="px-4 mt-auto w-full flex justify-center">
            <button class="w-full py-2 border border-green-500/50 text-green-400 rounded hover:bg-green-500/10 transition-colors text-sm font-mono flex justify-center items-center">
                <span class="cv-long">Descargar CV</span>
                <span class="cv-short font-bold">CV</span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </aside>
    
    <main class="flex-1 h-screen overflow-y-auto relative">
      
        <div id="mobile-overlay" class="fixed inset-0 bg-gray-950/80 backdrop-blur-sm z-40 hidden opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
      
      <section id="inicio" class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full relative overflow-hidden py-24 px-8 lg:px-12">
        <div class="text-center z-30 mb-12 lg:mb-16 mt-8">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-mono text-green-500 mb-4 tracking-tight">> Hello World_</h1>
            <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-gray-300 font-medium">Soy <span class="font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-gray-400">Carlos Bravo Sánchez</span>,</p>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-green-400/80 font-mono mt-2 font-semibold">Ingeniero Informático</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10 gap-12 md:gap-0 mt-8 lg:mt-16">
            
            <div id="box-ia" class="flex-1 w-full min-w-0 relative group z-10 md:-mr-12">
                <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-gray-900 rounded-3xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-75 transition duration-500"></div>
                <div class="relative w-full min-h-[450px] bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-6 xl:p-12 cursor-default shadow-2xl flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center tracking-tight">Inteligencia <span class="text-green-500">Artificial</span></h2>
                    
                    <div id="ia-carousel" class="w-full flex-1 bg-gray-950 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 overflow-hidden relative group/carousel">
                        {inicioImagesIA.map((img, index) => (
                            <img src={img.src} alt={img.alt} class={`carousel-img absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-700 ${index === 0 ? 'opacity-100' : 'opacity-0'} z-0`} />
                        ))}
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-950 via-gray-900/40 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
                        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-0 w-full z-20 pointer-events-none text-center px-4">
                            <p class="ia-carousel-text text-gray-300 text-sm font-mono font-semibold shadow-black drop-shadow-md transition-opacity duration-300">
                                {inicioImagesIA[0].text}
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mt-3">
                                {inicioImagesIA.map(() => (
                                    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden"><div class="progress-bar-fill"></div></div>
                                ))}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button id="ia-prev" class="absolute left-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-gray-900/80 hover:bg-green-500 text-white hover:text-gray-950 p-2 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover/carousel:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 z-30 border border-gray-600 hover:border-transparent">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                        <button id="ia-next" class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-gray-900/80 hover:bg-green-500 text-white hover:text-gray-950 p-2 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover/carousel:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 z-30 border border-gray-600 hover:border-transparent">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-80 h-[32rem] relative flex-shrink-0 z-20 hidden md:block pointer-events-none perspective-1000">
                <img id="center-avatar" src="/avatar-neutral.png" alt="Carlos Bravo" class="w-full h-full object-contain transition-all duration-300" />
            </div>

            <div id="box-quantum" class="flex-1 w-full min-w-0 relative group z-10 md:-ml-12">
                <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-gray-900 rounded-3xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-75 transition duration-500"></div>
                <div class="relative w-full min-h-[450px] bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-6 xl:p-12 cursor-default shadow-2xl flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8 text-center tracking-tight">Computación <span class="text-green-500">Cuántica</span></h2>
                    
                    <div id="q-carousel" class="w-full flex-1 bg-gray-950 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700 overflow-hidden relative group/carousel">
                        {inicioImagesQuantum.map((img, index) => (
                            <img src={img.src} alt={img.alt} class={`carousel-img absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-opacity duration-700 ${index === 0 ? 'opacity-100' : 'opacity-0'} z-0`} />
                        ))}
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-950 via-gray-900/40 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
                        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-0 w-full z-20 pointer-events-none text-center px-4">
                            <p class="q-carousel-text text-gray-300 text-sm font-mono font-semibold shadow-black drop-shadow-md transition-opacity duration-300">
                                {inicioImagesQuantum[0].text}
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex justify-center gap-2 mt-3">
                                {inicioImagesQuantum.map(() => (
                                    <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-gray-700 rounded-full overflow-hidden"><div class="progress-bar-fill"></div></div>
                                ))}
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button id="q-prev" class="absolute left-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-gray-900/80 hover:bg-green-500 text-white hover:text-gray-950 p-2 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover/carousel:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 z-30 border border-gray-600 hover:border-transparent">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                        <button id="q-next" class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-gray-900/80 hover:bg-green-500 text-white hover:text-gray-950 p-2 rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover/carousel:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 z-30 border border-gray-600 hover:border-transparent">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="sobre-mi" class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full relative border-t border-gray-800 py-24 px-8 lg:px-12">
        <div class="max-w-6xl w-full flex flex-col">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-12"><span class="text-green-500 font-mono">01.</span> Sobre mí</h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
                
                <div class="flex-1 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    <p class="mb-6">
                        La ingeniería consiste en <span class="text-green-500 font-medium">resolver problemas</span> complejos de la forma más eficiente posible. Esa filosofía me ha llevado desde idear y optimizar algoritmos hasta trabajar con <span class="text-green-500 font-medium">redes neuronales</span> profundas y diseñar <span class="text-green-500 font-medium">arquitecturas multiagente</span>.
